com.fortyoneconcepts.valjogen.model

Class Configuration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fortyoneconcepts.valjogen.model.Configuration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConfigurationOptionKeys

    public final class Configuration
extends Object
implements ConfigurationOptionKeys
    Contains methods that return the effective configuration taking processor options and annotated elements into account. All getters return simple values. No nulls are ever returned.
